text: Norma Icardi (born 16 August 1930) is an Italian gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1930 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Italian female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Italy Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Trieste
